    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In masonry, a soft brick sometimes used for facing because of the ease with which it can be cut or rubbed smooth.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
